name: Relaxing Harpies 25/25
description:
“Relaxing Harpies”
Oil on canvas
22×28 inches.

Two strange looking women, which are enjoying each other’s company, have wings and claws. These creatures are Harpies and symbolize inner demons. They appear calm and nonthreatening. They might be dormant at the moment, but will strike when the time is right.
